I'm thinking it may be related to: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3675144/regex-error-nothing-to-repeat given that the line here:

```
File "/scratch0/Softwares/pytorch_new/torch/lib/ATen/code_template.py", line 15, in CodeTemplate
'(^[^\n\S])?$([^\d\W]\w|{,?[^\d\W]\w*,?})', re.MULTILINE)
